<div class="block-contributor">
		

		<div class="block-contributor-content">
		<div class="block-contributor-bio small">
			<p><strong><span class="smallcaps">Akhim Yuseff Cabey</span></strong> was raised in the Bronx and now lives in Columbus, Ohio, where he will spend the summer gardening, grilling, and golfing. He won a Pushcart Prize in 2008 and is currently working on a memoir called <em>Little Red Love Machine</em>.</p><a href="/contributors/akhim-yuseff-cabey" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
	</div>
</div>

